spec: v0.6
name: helloworld
unikraft: stable
targets:
  # Developer machines (QEMU) - primary for local drun-001 / drun-002 loop
  - qemu/x86_64
  - qemu/arm64
  # Production path (Firecracker) - what the real dvr daemon will use
  - fc/x86_64

# A classic minimal Unikraft "Hello World" application.
# First `dvr unikernel build` will fetch the core + libraries (one-time, network).
# After that, builds and runs are fast and fully offline.
# This exercises the full local kraft integration for drun-001.